  "title": "表示不可能的情况",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"ZTCRFfYy\">数学中经常需要处理不可能的情况（比如使用反证法证明时）。在<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Explorable_explanation\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">可探索的解释</a><sup data-text=\"可探索的解释\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/598332415\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>中，如何可靠地表示这些不可能的情况？</p><p data-pid=\"9STP46zk\">如果你要用反证法证明，你必须找个办法来在视觉上呈现不可能的情况！</p><h3>参见</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"cUmXspDz\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Finiteness_assumption_in_explorable_media\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">可探索媒介中的有限对象假设</a></li></ul><h3>链接到本文</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"UILbnhsw\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Finiteness_assumption_in_explorable_media\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">可探索媒介的有限对象假设</a> ‎ (<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DSpecial%3AWhatLinksHere%26target%3DFiniteness%2Bassumption%2Bin%2Bexplorable%2Bmedia\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">← 链接</a>)<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"tNDN5Q-h\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Explorable_explanation\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">可探索的解释</a> ‎ (<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DSpecial%3AWhatLinksHere%26target%3DExplorable%2Bexplanation\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">← 链接</a>)</li></ul><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"t1wXkfR3\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 shom<br/>原文：<a h